Run Options

Source: R/clustTMB.R
run.options.Rd

Run Options

run.options(check.input = NULL, run.model = NULL, do.sdreport = NULL)

Arguments

check.input

TRUE: Return initial values before running TMB

run.model

FALSE: Return TMB object before optimizing model

do.sdreport

TRUE: Run delta method to obtain standard errors

Value

list

Examples

run.options()
#> $check.input
#> [1] FALSE
#> 
#> $run.model
#> [1] TRUE
#> 
#> $do.sdreport
#> [1] TRUE
#>
